3
00:01:00,190 --> 00:01:05,390
than five, dragged a raven-haired girl an
inch taller and a year older down the sea

4
00:01:05,390 --> 00:01:08,150
lane toward a small cottage.

5
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:13,670
The dark-haired girl’s lungs were sputtering,
