22
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,480
“Evie . . . what—”

23
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:23,820
“A broken rib. Maybe a punctured lung.”
She laid the girl in her bed and ripped the

24
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:29,230
girl’s bodice to her navel. Blood under
the skin showed black across the expanse of

25
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:35,590
the little girl’s ribs, fissures like spiderwebs
