58
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:23,350
it was almost nothing at all.

59
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:30,050
The mother wept, wishing for her sister—the
strongest witch. Healer of Kings, reviving

60
00:05:30,050 --> 00:05:35,321
those in power who turn a blind eye to magic
when their lives depend on it, but banish

61
00:05:35,321 --> 00:05:40,759
it when it doesn’t. She was the reason the
physician might come at all—though he would

62
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:47,470
be too late. As would Hansa, a day away, healing
