00:12:29,329 --> 00:12:37,730
to rescue him. Pleading. Silently calling
my name across the distance—Evvvvvvieee.

143
00:12:37,730 --> 00:12:43,009
I am the only one who can save him. Every
youth in town is here, but no one else can

144
00:12:43,009 --> 00:12:49,749
