provide. Mounted proudly to the mainmast,
half-harpoon, half-rifle, my darting gun looks

788
01:05:51,539 --> 01:05:55,150
as shiny and perfect as I’d hoped.

789
01:05:55,150 --> 01:05:59,210
Father hugs me close. “My Evelyn, the inventor.”

790
01:05:59,210 --> 01:06:06,039
“It was nothing,” I say, though we both
know that’s not true. It took me the whole

791
01:06:06,039 --> 01:06:11,120
winter to create one from an old rifle and
modified harpoon, but if my calculations are

792
01:06:11,120 --> 01:06:16,720
correct, the contraption will send out both
a bomb lance and a tether harpoon, narrowing

793
01:06:16,720 --> 01:06:22,510
the chances of a whale escaping. If all goes
