IT’S A PERFECT NIGHT FOR BURNING WITCHES.

822
01:08:39,660 --> 01:08:46,150
That’s what Sankt Hans Aften is, after all.
A celebration in the name of ridding people

823
01:08:46,150 --> 01:08:51,890
like me from this earth through flames, drowning,
banishment—whatever seemed right at the

824
01:08:51,890 --> 01:08:52,890
time.

