854
01:11:30,871 --> 01:11:33,680
I bashed my leg on that rock at ten.”

855
01:11:33,680 --> 01:11:38,910
I nearly laugh, thinking of Nik passing out
at the sight of his own blood. Right in the

856
01:11:38,910 --> 01:11:44,230
middle of a trail leading up Lille Bjerg Pass.
Anna and I stripped off our stockings and

857
01:11:44,230 --> 01:11:48,800
tied them tightly above the gash across his
