878
01:13:15,080 --> 01:13:19,410
by my side, this year I play along alone.

879
01:13:19,410 --> 01:13:24,790
I suppose I could join the castle workers—I’ve
known them since I was a small child. But

880
01:13:24,790 --> 01:13:30,760
I’m not truly one of them. And the other
