896
01:14:28,060 --> 01:14:30,830
against the horrors of witchcraft.

897
01:14:30,830 --> 01:14:38,100
The queen is a beauty by any measure, all
fine bone structure and swanlike grace. Her

898
01:14:38,100 --> 01:14:43,230
hair is curled and coiled atop her head, a
deep blond halo around a crown of sapphires

899
01:14:43,230 --> 01:14:49,620
and diamonds. When she steps forward in the
sand, she looks every bit a painting in the

900
01:14:49,620 --> 01:14:50,620
firelight.

901
01:14:50,620 --> 01:14:55,750
