Kingdoms because of the courage of King Christian

912
01:15:47,600 --> 01:15:54,230
IV. We live in safety and harmony because
of the laws he put in place. Witchcraft has

913
01:15:54,230 --> 01:15:57,870
no place except in the depths of hell.”

914
01:15:57,870 --> 01:16:02,980
The queen hoists the red doll above her head
so hard its little witch’s hat falls, the

915
01:16:02,980 --> 01:16:09,060
fire sucking it into the flames. “Shall
there be any devils on our shores, know you

916
01:16:09,060 --> 01:16:16,820
