on the spot, tossing the witch into the bonfire—royally

920
01:16:30,190 --> 01:16:35,130
ousting us because our power is a threat to
her own.

921
01:16:35,130 --> 01:16:41,880
We are to form an orderly line circling the
fire, but I can’t do that. I won’t do

922
01:16:41,880 --> 01:16:47,160
