to her when they burn their skin, grateful

931
01:17:33,660 --> 01:17:38,170
for her ancient medicinal treatments, turn
little wooden replicas of our ancestors to

932
01:17:38,170 --> 01:17:45,330
ash each year on this date. And she just laughs
