943
01:18:32,460 --> 01:18:39,040
Urda and give thanks for her blessings and
bounty, be it from the sea or from land.”

944
01:18:39,040 --> 01:18:44,351
The fire crackles happily behind him, the
tallest flames licking at the stars. Despite

945
01:18:44,351 --> 01:18:49,310
the crush of people, only that crackle and
