951
01:19:17,010 --> 01:19:18,830
has suddenly returned.

952
01:19:18,830 --> 01:19:25,930
“These next four days are a celebration.
Games, races, songs, and feasts in our goddess’s

953
01:19:25,930 --> 01:19:33,820
name. Let us not forget that it is all for
her. It is fun. It is merry. But it has a

954
01:19:33,820 --> 01:19:37,090
utility—a reason. Urda.”

955
01:19:37,090 --> 01:19:42,810
There is an audible gasp in the crowd—Nik
has gone off script. He’s speaking from

956
01:19:42,810 --> 01:19:45,090
the heart, and I couldn’t be prouder.

957
01:19:45,090 --> 01:19:51,980
“Last year, we did the same as we will do
