978
01:21:43,090 --> 01:21:45,310
can give.”

979
01:21:45,310 --> 01:21:52,550
Nik pauses, his coal-dark eyes on the harbor
over our heads. I realize he’s referencing

980
01:21:52,550 --> 01:21:58,780
Anna too. Honoring her as something Urda claimed
for her own, the sea doing the goddess’s

981
01:21:58,780 --> 01:21:59,780
bidding.

