996
01:23:32,860 --> 01:23:36,600
Nik is swallowed by their affections.

997
01:23:36,600 --> 01:23:41,720
And though I wait on the beach for him to
resurface, he doesn’t. Whisked away for

998
01:23:41,720 --> 01:23:46,970
the night in a crowd of his subjects. Every
