1017
01:25:05,100 --> 01:25:10,960
would materialize among the gentle rolling
waves. Just suddenly appear with Iker aboard,

1018
01:25:10,960 --> 01:25:16,820
a shine in his eyes and laughter on his lips.
That he’d jump off the bow before anchoring,

1019
01:25:16,820 --> 01:25:22,190
not able to hold himself back from me a moment
longer. That he’d pull me in deeply into

1020
01:25:22,190 --> 01:25:24,040
his arms for another kiss.

1021
01:25:24,040 --> 01:25:27,660
I blink and the thought has vanished.

1022
01:25:27,660 --> 01:25:30,750
