1024
01:25:34,480 --> 01:25:39,010
I step off the dock, my back to the waves
that took Anna, my head and heart throbbing

1025
01:25:39,010 --> 01:25:44,460
with the wish that she would return, too.
That I’d have my friend back. That I wouldn’t

1026
01:25:44,460 --> 01:25:49,060
feel the need to pin my hopes on boys who
I should’ve known all along would only care

1027
01:25:49,060 --> 01:25:54,720
about me until they hit that invisible line
