1029
01:25:58,970 --> 01:26:05,010
I am too restless to run home to bed. To nod
and smile at Hansa’s drunken tale of her

1030
01:26:05,010 --> 01:26:09,710
grand evening with her grand friends—as
if those friends didn’t just burn thousands

1031
01:26:09,710 --> 01:26:16,760
of us. So I walk along the water to the cove
