1035
01:26:32,640 --> 01:26:37,430
I do have friends who aren’t royal. I do.

1036
01:26:37,430 --> 01:26:41,600
I have the kids from school who tolerate me
for Nik’s sake, but only really when their

1037
01:26:41,600 --> 01:26:48,350
prince is around. But for the most part, all
I see when I greet their faces is the disapproval

1038
01:26:48,350 --> 01:26:50,640
reflected in their eyes.

1039
01:26:50,640 --> 01:26:54,000
That girl—couldn’t save her mother.

1040
01:26:54,000 --> 01:26:57,480
That girl—lived while her best friend drowned.

1041
01:26:57,480 --> 01:27:02,240
That girl—thinks her father’s job gives
