from well past the harbor and deep within

1062
01:28:48,730 --> 01:28:49,730
the sea.

1063
01:28:49,730 --> 01:28:55,161
I am suddenly awake, and I turn my attention
again to the rock wall. But there’s nothing

1064
01:28:55,161 --> 01:28:57,480
to see but shadow and waves.

1065
01:28:57,480 --> 01:29:02,380
Maybe it was the octopus who’s made the
cove his home, taunting me the same way he

1066
01:29:02,380 --> 01:29:07,190
taunts Tante Hansa, who would like nothing
