1069
01:29:13,010 --> 01:29:15,170
Just as they must have on Nik’s birthday.

1070
01:29:15,170 --> 01:29:20,651
“Perhaps you need to avoid the cove when
the moon is strong, Evelyn,” I mutter. The

1071
01:29:20,651 --> 01:29:23,680
moon can do funny things to a witch.

