1113
01:32:47,340 --> 01:32:48,340
his sights.

1114
01:32:48,340 --> 01:32:53,520
Moving forward, he turned his head as much
as the weight and struggle would allow, hoping

1115
01:32:53,520 --> 01:32:56,610
for a flash of blond safely at the sandbar.

1116
01:32:56,610 --> 01:32:58,580
He saw nothing.

1117
01:32:58,580 --> 01:33:04,060
On the shore, he called as loud as he could
for help. He set Evie on the sand, brushing

1118
01:33:04,060 --> 01:33:07,190
back her curls, ear to her mouth.

1119
01:33:07,190 --> 01:33:09,610
No breath.

1120
01:33:09,610 --> 01:33:14,650
He rolled her over and pounded on her back.
