1131
01:33:58,490 --> 01:33:59,660
“Nik?”

1132
01:33:59,660 --> 01:34:03,170
“Yes! Evie, yes!”

1133
01:34:03,170 --> 01:34:08,860
Smiling briefly, he hugged her close then,
even if it was inappropriate, with her bare-shouldered

1134
01:34:08,860 --> 01:34:15,150
in her petticoat and him a prince. But he
