1148
01:35:15,310 --> 01:35:20,980
as this one, it is not hard to conjure the
words for Urda, yet I can’t help but think

1149
01:35:20,980 --> 01:35:28,560
back to Nik’s speech. No magic can trick
her. No words can ply her. No will can sway

1150
01:35:28,560 --> 01:35:36,110
her. Is my spell a trick? A panic suddenly
seizes me. My heart beats fast and my feet

1151
01:35:36,110 --> 01:35:43,980
feel like lead. The dock begins to spin before
my eyes. Is this my punishment? I close my

1152
01:35:43,980 --> 01:35:50,280
eyes to right my balance. I’m being silly.
My magic is not meant to deceive. My words

1153
01:35:50,280 --> 01:35:57,051
are intended to honor Urda, honor her sea.
