1159
01:36:24,310 --> 01:36:30,530
of samsø, a jar of pickled herring we call
slid, and a crusty loaf of rye bread so dense

1160
01:36:30,530 --> 01:36:35,220
it could pass as a sea stone—and return
to the Havnestad Cove.

1161
01:36:35,220 --> 01:36:40,960
It’s quiet here, just a few couples trailing
along the rocks, none taking any notice of

1162
01:36:40,960 --> 01:36:46,530
me. I remove my shoes and stockings and place
them in the same spot as yesterday, and I

1163
01:36:46,530 --> 01:36:51,090
hop between the smaller footstep islands to
the big one, Picnic Rock earning its name

1164
01:36:51,090 --> 01:36:57,230
yet again. The strong sun and calm tide has
