1165
01:36:57,230 --> 01:37:01,250
lie on my back, face to the sky, and shut
my eyes.

1166
01:37:01,250 --> 01:37:09,260
Though I don’t want it to, my mind shifts
to Iker. He still hasn’t returned. I am

1167
01:37:09,260 --> 01:37:14,730
already anxious, and the same panicky feeling
quickly returns.

1168
01:37:14,730 --> 01:37:16,560
What if something’s gone wrong?

1169
01:37:16,560 --> 01:37:18,380
What if the steam stack exploded?

1170
01:37:18,380 --> 01:37:21,930
