02:02:42,210 --> 02:02:44,710
HARD and takes a step toward me.

1478
02:02:44,710 --> 02:02:50,080
I instinctively take a step back, bumping
into the table behind me and knocking a corked

1479
02:02:50,080 --> 02:02:55,320
vial of octopus ink on its side. I’m not
