1500
02:04:49,740 --> 02:04:52,760
We will only survive our secrets together.

1501
02:04:52,760 --> 02:04:58,870
“I promise I won’t say a thing,” I assure
her, a hint of regret in my voice.

1502
02:04:58,870 --> 02:05:04,860
“Thank you,” she says. “My lips are
sealed too.” She weaves a slim finger through

1503
02:05:04,860 --> 02:05:11,190
