1512
02:05:57,020 --> 02:06:00,880
you humans think we are. I could not just
let him drown.”

1513
02:06:00,880 --> 02:06:07,700
Drown. Like Anna did. Like I thought Anna
did.

1514
02:06:07,700 --> 02:06:15,800
At this moment, Annemette looks so pretty.
So innocent. She raises her eyes to meet mine.

1515
02:06:15,800 --> 02:06:17,060
“Would you like to meet him?” I ask.

1516
02:06:17,060 --> 02:06:17,560
“Please,” she says.

